statements: SELECT * FROM real_estate_investment_portfolio;
SELECT property_name, acquisition_date, purchase_price FROM real_estate_investment_portfolio WHERE return_on_investment > 10.00;
SELECT property_id, property_name, sale_date, selling_price FROM real_estate_investment_portfolio ORDER BY sale_date DESC;
SELECT property_name, purchase_price, return_on_investment FROM real_estate_investment_portfolio WHERE return_on_investment < 5.00 ORDER BY purchase_price ASC;
SELECT * FROM real_estate_investment_portfolio WHERE acquisition_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT property_name, acquisition_date, selling_price FROM real_estate_investment_portfolio WHERE purchase_price > 500000 ORDER BY acquisition_date DESC;
SELECT property_name, sale_date, return_on_investment FROM real_estate_investment_portfolio WHERE sale_date IS NOT NULL AND return_on_investment > 5 ORDER BY return_on_investment DESC;
SELECT * FROM real_estate_investment_portfolio WHERE acquisition_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY property_id ASC;
SELECT property_name, purchase_price, return_on_investment FROM real_estate_investment_portfolio WHERE return_on_investment < 0 AND purchase_price > 100000 ORDER BY property_name ASC;
SELECT property_name, purchase_price, selling_price, return_on_investment FROM real_estate_investment_portfolio WHERE selling_price IS NULL OR return_on_investment IS NULL;
SELECT * FROM acquisitions ORDER BY purchase_date DESC;
SELECT property_name, purchase_price FROM acquisitions WHERE purchase_price > 100000 ORDER BY property_name ASC;
SELECT id, sale_price, sale_date FROM sales WHERE sale_price < 50000;
SELECT * FROM acquisitions WHERE property_name = 'ABC Property';
SELECT id, property_name FROM acquisitions WHERE purchase_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT * FROM acquisitions WHERE purchase_price > 50000 ORDER BY purchase_date DESC;
SELECT property_name, purchase_price FROM acquisitions WHERE purchase_price < 100000 ORDER BY property_name ASC;
SELECT id, property_name, purchase_price, purchase_date FROM acquisitions WHERE purchase_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT property_name, purchase_price, purchase_date FROM acquisitions WHERE purchase_price >= 75000 AND purchase_date < '2022-01-01' ORDER BY purchase_price DESC;
SELECT id, property_name, sale_price, sale_date FROM sales WHERE sale_price > 100000 ORDER BY sale_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM properties;
SELECT property_name, current_value FROM properties ORDER BY current_value DESC;
SELECT property_name, acquisition_date, acquisition_cost FROM properties WHERE acquisition_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT investor_name, email FROM investors WHERE phone_number LIKE '%555%';
SELECT * FROM transactions WHERE transaction_type = 'Purchase' ORDER BY transaction_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM properties WHERE acquisition_cost > 1000 ORDER BY acquisition_date DESC
SELECT property_id, property_name, current_value FROM properties WHERE return_on_investment < 10
SELECT investor_name, email FROM investors WHERE investor_id = 5
SELECT * FROM transactions WHERE transaction_amount BETWEEN 5000 AND 10000 AND transaction_date >= '2021-01-01' ORDER BY transaction_amount ASC
SELECT investor_id, investor_name, phone_number FROM investors
SELECT * FROM properties;
SELECT property_id, address, purchase_price FROM properties WHERE purchase_price > 500000;
SELECT owner_id, name, email FROM owners ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT transaction_id, transaction_type, transaction_date FROM transactions WHERE transaction_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT investment_id, owner_id, amount_invested, return_amount FROM investments WHERE amount_invested < 10000 ORDER BY return_amount DESC;
SELECT * FROM properties WHERE purchase_price > 100000 ORDER BY purchase_price DESC;
SELECT * FROM owners WHERE name LIKE '%Johnson%' AND email LIKE '%gmail.com';
SELECT p.address, t.transaction_type FROM properties p JOIN transactions t ON p.property_id = t.property_id;
SELECT i.owner_id, i.amount_invested, o.name FROM investments i JOIN owners o ON i.owner_id = o.owner_id WHERE i.amount_invested > 50000 ORDER BY i.amount_invested DESC;

SELECT t.transaction_date, t.transaction_type, p.address, o.name FROM transactions t JOIN properties p ON t.property_id = p.property_id JOIN owners o ON t.owner_id = o.owner_id WHERE t.transaction_date > '2020-01-01' ORDER BY t.transaction_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM property_acquisitions;
SELECT property_name, acquisition_date FROM property_acquisitions ORDER BY acquisition_date DESC;
SELECT id, property_name, purchase_price FROM property_acquisitions WHERE purchase_price > 500000;
SELECT property_name, sale_price FROM property_sales WHERE sale_price < 10000 ORDER BY sale_price ASC;
SELECT property_id, roi_percentage FROM return_on_investment WHERE return_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT * FROM property_acquisitions;
SELECT property_name, acquisition_date FROM property_acquisitions WHERE purchase_price > 10000 ORDER BY acquisition_date DESC;
SELECT property_name, purchase_price, DATE_FORMAT(acquisition_date, '%Y-%m-%d') AS formatted_date FROM property_acquisitions WHERE purchase_price BETWEEN 5000 AND 10000;

SELECT p.property_name, ROUND(r.roi_percentage, 2) AS rounded_roi FROM property_acquisitions p JOIN return_on_investment r ON p.id = r.property_id WHERE r.roi_percentage > 10 ORDER BY rounded_roi DESC;

SELECT pm.manager_id, po.owner_name, pa.property_name FROM property_management pm JOIN property_owners po ON pm.manager_id = po.owner_id JOIN property_acquisitions pa ON pm.property_id = pa.id ORDER BY pa.purchase_price ASC;
